(You going to reply to Modem being defeated by Obsidian?)

Lash:



Instinctively the robot ducked, two bullets flying overhead but one digging 
into the armor of his left shoulder.  Taking a step back from the impact he 
made quick calculations and a whip appeared in his hand.  Pressing a button 
it began to glow with electricity.  Lifting his arm back, he thrust it 
forward, attempting to wrap the whip around Penguin's neck.
